Mycelium is "so hot right now" in climate tech...

But in 2013? Not so much!

@MyocoWorksInc Co-Founder Sophia Wang joined @mollywood and broke down her amazing founding story: https://t.co/qmHL6Vpw32

next stop on @SBF_FTX's ill-advised media tour:

a date with Columbo... wait no that's @GStephanopoulos!

@mollywood &amp; @Jason react to the CLINIC put on by Mr. Stephanopoulos https://t.co/Tp85Axmtgz

.@SBF_FTX has been on a media tour the past few days!

first stop: #Dealbook

@jason &amp; @mollywood react to SBF's "i made a mistake" defense: https://t.co/MlfFWmsnjP

did you check your #SpotifyWrapped yet!?

of course you did.

@mollywood &amp; @_rachelbraun broke down some interesting new wrinkles in the 2022 edition of $SPOT's mega-viral hit https://t.co/fPvYVpAGr4

back when @Apple launched its App Store, a 70/30 revenue split made sense and was the best solution at the time

now... things have changed!

@mollywood &amp; @jason react to Steve Jobs debuting the App Store's 30% take rate back in 2008 https://t.co/DtcVRMbMnn

$AAPL and $GOOG have an app store duopoly

is that good or bad for startups and enterprises?

@jason &amp; @mollywood discuss: https://t.co/FkONqifYm3

.@pipe's co-founders all announced they were stepping down from day-to-day operations last week

since then, there have been a bunch of rumors and speculation around what happened...

@jason, @mollywood, and @alex try to get to the bottom of it: https://t.co/ovHkcgWfZN

via @BusinessInsider, $AMZN's Alexa / @PrimeVideo unit is on pace to lose $10B in 2022

MOST of those losses are coming from the Alexa / Echo hardware products

@jason has an idea for how to salvage the Alexa brand: open-source it! https://t.co/XA7GRk4mqG

EMERGENCY POD IS LIVE!

@RobertIger is BACK as $DIS CEO...

@lons joins @jason &amp; @mollywood to break down what Iger's second stint as CEO might look like:
-- potential $NFLX merger?
-- going all-in on live content?
-- reversing price gouging at parks? https://t.co/GHLCR1AJeu

